      <title>印度最大影子银行巴贾杰寻求高达 5 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/india-s-biggest-shadow-bank-bajaj-seeks-up-to-500-million-loan</link>
