      <title>凯雷推迟亚洲并购基金募资，因日本基金需求下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/carlyle-delays-asia-buyout-fund-close-as-japan-pool-saps-demand</link>
